  "system": {
    "description": "<p>Sometimes called a 'light cruiser', the heavy frigate pushes a frigate hull to its engineering maximum. Its torpedo launcher (carrying 16 torpedoes' worth of reload stock) can threaten even cruiser-class enemies, and its heavy crew complement and drop pod let it dispatch marines to hot spots quickly. Its armor is still inferior to a true cruiser's.</p><p><strong>Crew:</strong> 30/120. <strong>Cost:</strong> 9.783M base price, 489,150cr six-month maintenance, 3.942M yearly crew cost (90 crew).</p>",
